-- Warlord Linked to Al-Qaeda Confirmed Dead in Mali, France Says
-- B y   A l a n   K a t z
-- 2013-03-23T15:21:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-23/warlord-linked-to-al-qaeda-confirmed-dead-in-mali-france-says.html
Abou Zeid, an al-Qaeda in Islamic
Maghreb commander, was killed in  Mali  in February, the French
government confirmed today.  Zeid died in combat with French troops in northern Mali,
the French president’s office said an e-mailed statement. French
officials have said since early March that it was likely that he
was dead.  The death marks “a major step” in the fight against
terrorism in the Sahel region, according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alan Katz in Paris at 
